return ['messages'=>['19749cc0e34a76f58098d89d7e71e147'=>'In addition, you will obtain an artistic result of your own process, where you will be able to observe your own power and healing, from an external perspective full of love.','324a69feee8843f979d7cc3c065b5524'=>'<em>It\'s always in you.</em>','444705c9a9b3c35e42801048cfeb3f29'=>'<em>Healing photo sessions</em> are a way to delve deeper into those emotions, allowing you to observe and express them in a healthy and beautiful way. ','5da0602780ba72753f61e16967a8d23e'=>'Since we are little, we tent to feel with great intensity, however, we are very rarely taught how to manage it. ','698ad83534598a4fe6600e50e145cf20'=>'We grow up, we hit that maelstrom called adolescence and then we force ourselves to hide those emotions in order to fit into society.','9a9df6ef43c2a5c516ffe08027ca2f42'=>'We reach adulthood without having the slightest idea of ​​what those emotions are trying to tell us, or how to manage our reactions.','9f8031eed3ff050a5c683daaa05345aa'=>'We usually follow two opposite paths: Either we choose to keep everything to ourselves, because we force ourselves to believe that it is not important, or we explode at the slightest thing, all the time, with everyone, because we feel that everything is personal.','<em>Está siempre en ti.</em>'=>'<em>It\'s always in you.</em>','<em>Las sesiones de fotos sanadoras</em> son una forma de profundizar en esas emociones, permitiéndote  observarlas y expresarlas de una manera sana y hermosa. '=>'<em>Healing photo sessions</em> are a way to delve deeper into those emotions, allowing you to observe and express them in a healthy and beautiful way. ','Además de que obtendrás un resultado artístico de tu propio proceso, donde podrás observar tu propio poder y sanación, desde una mirada exterior llena de amor.'=>'In addition, you will obtain an artistic result of your own process, where you will be able to observe your own power and healing, from an external perspective full of love.','Crecemos, llegamos a esa vorágine llamada adolescencia y luego nos obligamos a nosotros mismos a esconder esas emociones con el fin de encajar en la sociedad.'=>'We grow up, we hit that maelstrom called adolescence and then we force ourselves to hide those emotions in order to fit into society.','Desde pequeños sentimos con gran intensidad, sin embargo, muy rara vez nos enseñan a gestionarlo. '=>'Since we are little, we tent to feel with great intensity, however, we are very rarely taught how to manage it. ','Es una experiencia que puede llegar a ser profundamente sanadora, si te permites ahondar en tu sombra, en tu alma, sin juzgar. Solo sintiendo y permitiendo que las emociones afloren en tu cuerpo y sean expresadas a través de él, en un ambiente seguro y de confianza donde podrás exteriorizar tu vulnerabilidad.'=>'It is an experience that can be deeply healing, if you allow yourself to delve into your shadow, into your soul, without judging. Just feeling and allowing the emotions to emerge in your body and be expressed through it, in a safe and trusting environment where you can externalize your vulnerability. ','Llegamos a la edad adulta sin tener ni puta idea de qué nos quieren decir esas emociones, o de cómo gestionar nuestras reacciones.'=>'We reach adulthood without having the slightest idea of ​​what those emotions are trying to tell us, or how to manage our reactions.','Pero realmente no muchos saben o entienden que realmente, nosotros mismos tenemos control sobre lo que sentimos; que la decisión es siempre nuestra, y se encuentra en nuestras manos decidir que X acontecimiento nos arruine la mañana, el día, la semana, el año o incluso la vida. '=>'But not many people really know or understand that we really do have control over what we feel; that the decision is always ours, and it is in our hands to decide that X event ruins our morning, our day, our week, our year or even our life. ','Se suelen seguir dos caminos opuestos: O optamos por guardarnos todo, porque nos obligamos a creer que no tiene importancia, o estallamos a la mínima, todo el tiempo, con todo el mundo, porque sentimos que todo es personal.'=>'We usually follow two opposite paths: Either we choose to keep everything to ourselves, because we force ourselves to believe that it is not important, or we explode at the slightest thing, all the time, with everyone, because we feel that everything is personal.','Y verlo no es nada sencillo (sobre todo porque hemos vivido toda nuestra vida aprendiendo miles de mecanismos de defensa que nos alejan de entenderlo), pero cuando por fin logras entenderlo, te das cuenta de que no hay nada más obvio que eso.'=>'And seeing it is not easy at all (especially because we have lived our entire lives learning thousands of defense mechanisms that keep us from understanding it), but when you finally manage to understand it, you realize that there is nothing more obvious than that.','ad5fa2ad00ce9f92a31241cc8e587f39'=>'But not many people really know or understand that we really do have control over what we feel; that the decision is always ours, and it is in our hands to decide that X event ruins our morning, our day, our week, our year or even our life. ','ea27dc9d8f96451c28b0350ea196c204'=>'It is an experience that can be deeply healing, if you allow yourself to delve into your shadow, into your soul, without judging. Just feeling and allowing the emotions to emerge in your body and be expressed through it, in a safe and trusting environment where you can externalize your vulnerability. ','f14af9e0f82ccb797d37f6966814feaf'=>'healing session','fcc0cb60f2f668a7ce7a4d73f9283392'=>'And seeing it is not easy at all (especially because we have lived our entire lives learning thousands of defense mechanisms that keep us from understanding it), but when you finally manage to understand it, you realize that there is nothing more obvious than that.','sesión sanadora'=>'healing session']];
